Task 3:

Create a new view file and give a name as mentioned in the lab instruction page.

Remove all default code and add this code in the file by replacing the view file name with VIEW_NAME:


view: VIEW_NAME {
extension: required

dimension: id {
primary_key: yes
type: number
sql: ${TABLE}.id ;;
}

dimension: email {
type: string
sql: ${TABLE}.email ;;
}

dimension: first_name {
type: string
sql: ${TABLE}.first_name ;;
}

dimension: last_name {
type: string
sql: ${TABLE}.last_name ;;
}

dimension: latitude {
type: number
sql: ${TABLE}.latitude ;;
}

dimension: longitude {
type: number
sql: ${TABLE}.longitude ;;
}
}
